<p><strong><em>BRT Realengo-Madureira (TransIntendente)<br /></em></strong>( <a href="https://desafioagorario.crowdicity.com/post/88386" target="_blank">https://desafioagorario.crowdicity.com/post/88386</a> )</p>
<p><strong><em>Via Carioca: Monotrilho no Caminho Imperial</em></strong> – Usuário <strong>Quero Metrô<br /></strong>( <a href="https://desafioagorario.crowdicity.com/post/97100" target="_blank">https://desafioagorario.crowdicity.com/post/97100</a> )</p>
